sights(planId)`.\\n- Renders a list of insight cards. Each card shows:\\n  - Severity indicator (color-coded badge: 'high' = red, 'medium' = amber, 'low' = blue).\\n  - Insight text.\\n  - Action suggestion (italicized, lighter text).\\n  - Source entity links (clickable).\\n  - AiFeedbackButtons with the suggestion's ID.\\n- Loading state: skeleton cards (use Skeleton component from ui/).\\n- Empty state: \\\"No AI insights available for this period.\\\"\\n- Error state: \\\"Failed to load insights\\\" message.\\n- aiAvailable=false state: subtle disabled message (same pattern as AiLintPanel unavailable state).\\n- data-testid: `insight-panel`, `insight-card-{id}`, `insight-panel-loading`, `insight-panel-empty`, `insight-panel-unavailable`.\\n\\nCreate `frontend/src/__tests__/InsightPanel.test.tsx`:\\n- Mock `ragHooks.ts`.\\n- Test renders insight cards for team mode.\\n- Test renders insight cards for personal mode.\\n- Test loading state.\\n- Test empty state.\\n- Test error state.\\n- Test aiAvailable=false state.\\n- Test AiFeedbackButtons rendered per card.\",\n  \"requiredChecks\": [\n    \"typecheck\",\n    \"unit\"\n  ]\n}\n\nThis is relay round 2. Another agent has already worked on this step.\n\nYou are in VERIFICATION MODE. Your default action is to APPROVE.\nFocus your review on the DIFF — the changes made in the previous round.\nOnly make changes if there is a MATERIAL defect: failing check, missing step requirement, logic bug, or security issue.\nStyle preferences, alternative approaches, comment wording, and optional polish are NOT grounds for changes.\n\nIf all checks pass and the step requirements are met, approve immediately.\nLog anything else you notice as observations — do not act on them.\n\nPrevious agent's notes:\n661 tests across 39 test files, all passing. Typecheck clean. Here's a summary:\n\n## Summary\n\n### `frontend/src/components/ai/InsightPanel.tsx` (new)\n\n- **Props**: discriminated union — `mode: 'team'` with optional `teamId` + 